{
  "stem": "5516.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this man who they threw over, Smetona, he was acquainted with a Jewish-- two brothers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Their name was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They was contractors.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they was comfortable people, rich people, and they knew him-- that when they threw him out from his position, they gave him a beautiful home.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they supported him with his family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after a while, he took over the government back from this guy who took over from him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he became president.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was president all the time till the Russian come over in 1940 when they took over the country.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I saw even when he left-- my store was across from his palace.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I saw his family and cars, they left for the German border.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from-- Germany let him in because they had agreement with the Russian government when they took it over to let him out, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they let them out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he come over in Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after from Germany, he left for United States.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was living in Chicago.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in Chicago was a fire.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in fire, he was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] burned up in fire.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So because of those Jews being nice to him, then he--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--was good to the Jews?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he was, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When even he president, these Jews, these two, they helped him a lot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, this is not official.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we know he's-- they helped him in all kind advice, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and he was very nice to Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We used to even call them [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] our father.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
